End-to-end setup from SSH key generation â†’ GitHub auth â†’ GCP Secret â†’ BigQuery Repository link.

ğŸ§© 0ï¸âƒ£ Set these variables first
# === ğŸ“ Replace these values ===
export GITHUB_USER="<your-github-username>"              # e.g. anuanurag2410
export GITHUB_REPO="<your-github-repo-name>"             # e.g. data-engineering-bootcamp
