âš¡ Troubleshooting
Issue	Fix
âŒ host public key didnâ€™t match	Re-run the ssh-keyscan command and paste the fresh line again
âŒ access token ... was rejected	You accidentally used an HTTPS URL â€” switch to SSH URL (git@github.com:...)
âŒ permission denied (publickey)	Make sure you added your public key in GitHub with write access
âŒ secret access denied	Re-run the add-iam-policy-binding step for the same secret